                <head>
                    <hi rend="italic">Editorial Note</hi>
                </head>
                <p>On May 17, President Truman approved and directed the implementation of <gloss
                        target="#t_NSC1">NSC</gloss> 48/5, “United States Objectives, Policies, and
                    Courses of Action in Asia.” A number of sections of this paper deal with United
                    States policy toward Japan. For text, see <ref target="#pg_33">page
                    33</ref>.</p>
            </div>
